  <brief_title>Lavender Oil on Preoperative Anxiety and Sedation Requirement in General Anaesthesia</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Lavender Oil on Preoperative Anxiety and Requirement of Propofol for Induction in Patients for General Anesthesia in Elective Surgeries in Hospital Kuala Lumpur</official_title>
